    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\nWhen i try to open a file inside: app\\\\(login)\\\\_layout.tsx \r\nneovim open the file without the path separator: app(login)\\\\_layout.tsx, and the file is empty.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/66179578/236712030-21283c5e-f47c-4c19-9f66-5229d3e747f2.png)\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThat the file path is opened with the separator.\r\nBefore: app(login\\\\_layout.tsx\r\nAfter: app\\\\(login)\\\\_layout.tsx",
