            "body": "> So what's the final recommendation here? using `bufadd()` / `bufload()`?\n\nyup. AFAICT, they could avoid all that pain with the approach I mentioned:\n\n```lua\nlocal bnr = vim.fn.bufadd(vim.fs.normalize(...))\nvim.cmd('buffer '..tostring(bnr))\n```",
